title: Living Breakthrough Minded | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Living Breakthrough Minded | Joel Osteen
description:
Your dreams may look impossible, but the God of breakthrough is working behind the scenes to arrange things in your favor. Even when you don’t see a way, He's getting ready to overwhelm you with His goodness.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
